; Coverage for textual_xacts.cc line 352: skip virtual posts in effective date
; balance assertion computation

2024/01/01=2024/01/15 Opening
    Assets:Checking    $500
    Equity:Opening

2024/01/05=2024/01/12 Virtual deposit
    (Assets:Checking)  $200

2024/01/02=2024/01/10 Deposit
    Assets:Checking    $100 = $100
    Income:Salary

test --effective reg Assets:Checking
24-Jan-15 Opening               Assets:Checking                $500         $500
24-Jan-12 Virtual deposit       (Assets:Checking)              $200         $700
24-Jan-10 Deposit               Assets:Checking                $100         $800
end test
